  1\. Acetaldehyde           0.0    0.0    0.0
  2\. Vinyl alcohol          9.1    9.6   13.5
  3\. Hydroxyethylidene     50.8   51.2   54.0

  : Comparison of the fitted potential energy surfaces and ab initio
